videos.description: Royce O'Neale knocks down a contested 3-pointer from the corner to give the Jazz a 14-0 lead over the Warriors.

videos.description: Steph Curry freezes Rudy Gobert with his handle and then quickly flips a shot up and in.

videos.description: Joe Ingles stops Kelly Oubre Jr. on the fast break, and Steve Kerr is assessed a technical foul for arguing the play.

videos.description: Steph Curry knocks down a trey to tie Reggie Miller on the all-time 3-point list.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Steph hits triple to tie Miller for 2nd on all-time list) 2021/1/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Steph hits triple to tie Miller for 2nd on all-time list

videos.description: With his fourth triple of the game, Steph Curry passes Reggie Miller to move into second place for the most 3-pointers made in NBA history. Ray Allen sits atop the list.
